# Next.js Platform Admin App (apps/admin)

This is the platform-operator administrative dashboard.
Stack: Next.js 15 (App Router), React 19, Tailwind CSS, Radix UI.

## Guidelines
- **Audience:** This is strictly for platform operators and support staff, not tenants or customers.
- **Component Creation:** Use functional components with Tailwind CSS. Place reusable UI components in `src/components/ui/`.
- **Architecture Boundary:** NEVER import from `apps/web`. The admin app communicates with `packages/api/src/modules/platform-admin/` routes.
- **Security:** Ensure all administrative actions trigger appropriate audit logs via backend endpoints.
